{"tid":1944643,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口交部：必須回應抹黑中國言行　但不回應美軍南海發射導彈及台海演練","createTime":"2020-03-26T13:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T14:09:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0721784bf0821b0c0deb069e3222725eafa3101","tid":1944643,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"外交部：必須回應抹黑中國言行　中美合作才是發展基調<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516948-20200326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516948-20200326.htm&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4fce3315\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516948-20200326.htm&h=376127bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516948-20200326.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中美就新型肺炎的源頭引起爭議，外交部副部長羅照輝表示，近期由於美國一些政要採取污名化的不當言行，損害中美合作抗疫和合作的氣氛，不是中方願意看到，重申抹黑中國的言行，中方必須作出回應，強調新冠肺炎源頭是科學問題，中國1月時對武漢封城，是非常不容易但必要的決定，又說，湖北和武漢有中國人民的犧牲和付出，為世界抗疫嬴得時間，所獲取的寶貴經驗也是有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n羅照輝形容，抗擊疫情合作的國際合作總體順利，又說中美在務實合作方面，都在進行，中國疫情嚴重時，美國朝野包括公司民間等，都給中國提供好多支持和協助，認為中美在疫苗研發等方面的發展，都走在最前面，兩國合作對雙方和人類都有利，敦促美國與中國合作，協助合作才是中美關係發展的基調。<br />\n<br />\n另外，羅照輝表示，中國的輸入病例當中，9成是中國公民，當中4成是在海外回國的留學生。他表示，明白留學生在海外爆發疫情下，急於回國，但希望留學生和家長要權衡利弊，認為留學生在當前形勢下，留在當地比倉促回國好，已提醒駐當地的駐外使領館要與留學生和當地政府保持溝通，反對任何形式的歧視行為，及時為海外公民提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1761007.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Ffyrbt_673021%2Ft1761007.shtml&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=c3fab046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1761007.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1761580.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Ffyrbt_673021%2Ft1761580.shtml&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=bb59ac7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1761580.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n連續兩日記者會都冇提美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇記者問定唔夠膽答？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4f0030d6510cb7300c8894d00b71dabab2fb85","tid":1944643,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"超前部署！美第七艦隊南海首發飛彈 三度派電偵機臨港 嚴密監控解放軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1940050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1940050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c3f2fd5a392cb85b8501fe475419e9904264701c","tid":1944643,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:54:44.000Z","msg":"[美軍再來了]  南海美軍機再次飛近香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1938380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1938380</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cab1a5cbe04cbad4ec7fae6a9985efe0114377ff","tid":1944643,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"不要忘記<br />\n<br />\n16歲少女被輪姦懷孕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c0a08d3e7352630ed0b3377af69ee015cfc7136","tid":1944643,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"美軍驅逐艦周三駛經台海做演練<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1944044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1944044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1653ad08f8a95ab0cf8406c946656ba7eb8e753c","tid":1944643,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T1